es_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"OS: **Ubuntu 19.04**\r\nCMake: **3.15**\r\n\r\nPage: https://www.glfw.org/docs/latest/build_guide.html\r\n\r\nDocumentation states to use the `OPENGL_gl_LIBRARY` cache variable. However, this appears to be `null` (leads to undefined references during compilation) when using **CMake 3.15** on **Ubuntu 19.04**. Using the `OPENGL_LIBRARIES` result variable stated [here in the cmake.org documentation](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/latest/module/FindOpenGL.html) instead does work.\r\n\r\n**Doesn't work (current documentation)** `target_link_libraries(myapp ${OPENGL_gl_LIBRARY})`\r\n**Works** `target_link_libraries(myapp ${OPENGL_LIBRARIES})`\r\n\r\nI believe this will likely be an issue on other distributions aswell.","closed_by":{"login":"elmindreda","id":133714,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzcxNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/133714?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda","html_url":"https://github.com/elmindreda","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/1580/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/